<p><b><u>Storm the Hill:</u></b>
<ul style="list-style: none;">
  <li>IAVA has spent the month of March bringing our biggest activation to DC, Storm the Hill. Storm the Hill is IAVA's largest activation of members designed to bring the agenda of the community to elected officials.  This is a huge leadership and professional development training for veterans, another program that IAVA pioneered to further tell the story of our community.</li>
